name: Tus-demo
body:
basic on  [tus resumable-upload protocol](http://www.tus.io/protocols/resumable-upload.html)
but support more ranges uploading at the same time.
difference:
HEAD content-range : bytes=0-9,20-29/30 (tell client the '0-9' and '20-29' ranges have uploaded.)

Project was implemented with nodejs.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
